The paper discusses the combination of millimeter wave (mmWave) multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) systems and index modulation (IM) technique, which are related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer communication (cs.COM).
